---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Product Manager who turns ambitious SaaS ideas into revenues with a data-driven approach",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">🚀 About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p class="italic">
			👋 Hi, I'm Mattia — a Product Manager who turns ambitious SaaS ideas into revenues you can plot on a hockey-stick graph (and explain in one slide). My craft sits at the crossroads of curiosity, code and commercial sense: I mine user insight, translate it into measurable roadmaps, then rally designers and engineers until the KPI dashboard turns green.
		</p>

		<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-8 mb-3">🌟 Impact at a glance</h3>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li><strong>LeadsBridge</strong> – shipped 400+ API integrations, grew to 2,500 daily active teams and lifted ARPU × 4 in 18 months.</li>
			<li><strong>Product-Led Growth</strong> – built two engines that sliced time-to-value by 30% and kept churn under 4%.</li>
			<li><strong>Agile@Scale</strong> – rolled out frameworks that doubled release cadence while pushing team NPS to 70.</li>
		</ul>

		<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-8 mb-3">🛠️ My playbook</h3>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li><strong>Every sprint counts</strong> – backlog items map to OKRs so nobody ships in the dark.</li>
			<li><strong>Data beats opinion</strong> – experiments run, metrics decide; no vanity reports.</li>
			<li><strong>Teams first</strong> – cross-functional facilitation that melts silos and lets ideas win.</li>
			<li><strong>Accessibility by default</strong> – products must work for everyone, not just the statistical average.</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="mt-6">
			If you need a partner who can simplify complexity, inspire execution and nudge both investors and engineers in the same breath, let's talk.
		</p>

		<hr class="my-8 border-dashed" />

		<div class="bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[color:var(--color-accent-2)] text-center">
			<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✨ Ready to turn ideas into metrics that matter?</h3>
			<a
				href="https://cal.com/mattia/15min"
				class="py-2 px-4 bg-[color:var(--color-accent-2)] text-[color:var(--color-on-primary)] rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-medium"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				📞 Book a 15-minute call →
			</a>
			<p class="text-sm mt-2 italic text-[color:var(--color-text-subtle)]">
				(No boring slides — just sharp questions!)
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
